# Regulatory Monitoring

Guidelines for continuous scanning of regulatory sources, detecting changes, and maintaining situational awareness across jurisdictions.

## Source Categories

```text
Regulatory Intelligence Sources
├── Primary Legal Sources (registers, statutes, court opinions)
├── Regulatory Agency Communications (enforcement, guidance, bulletins)
├── Industry Bodies (SRO rules, standards, professional requirements)
├── Legislative Activity (bills, hearings, lobbying disclosures)
└── Enforcement Intelligence (penalties, consent decrees, exam schedules)
```

